                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                jcr:title="Take on new opportunities to learn, grow and reach higher ground"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/title/v2/title"
                                type="h3"
                                variant="h"/>
                            <text
                                cq:styleIds="[1659545825678]"
                                jcr:created="{Date}2022-12-09T17:34:50.014-05:00"
                                jcr:createdBy="chiucx"
                                jcr:lastModified="{Date}2023-02-02T15:22:14.648-05:00"
                                jcr:lastModifiedBy="kokajx"
                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p> We believe in self-directed growth and development, where employees set the goals they want to achieve. We supplement this individualized approach with companywide education and an investment in emerging leaders. One example is our Learn. Develop. Perform. (LDP) program which offers easily accessible, personalized development that's tailored to employees' interests.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>During our award-winning LDP Week, experts and AbbVie leaders from around the world come to speak–and you choose who you want to learn from, based on your own interests and career journey.&amp;nbsp;Our experts cover diverse topics, from cross-functional collaboration and business acumen to unconscious bias. Plus, every year you’ll find innovative approaches to learning. Past events included a 24-hour radio station, bite-sized learning through a YouTube channel and a TED event.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                        </par_13>
